author: The Current
description:
Watch Ruston Kelly play "Waiting to Love You" in studio
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Ruston Kelly’s new album, "Pale, Through the Window," released on Friday, Sept. 12, 2025, and just a few weeks later, Kelly visited The Current studio to play solo acoustic versions of songs from the new record. Watch the performance of "Waiting to Love You" above.

Musician
Ruston Kelly – vocals and guitar

author: The Current
description:
Danny Brown talking about the qualities he admires in Kendrick Lamar and Earl Sweatshirt.

Kendrick Lamar and Earl Sweatshirt are featured on Danny Brown’s 2016 album ‘Atrocity Exhibition,’ and Danny references them both on the track “Book of Daniel” off of his new album ‘Stardust.’
title: Danny Brown on what he admires about Kendrick Lamar and Earl Sweatshirt #dannybrown #kendricklamar
